Spam your followers/friends and get more of them with TwitterTool!
Or a less offensive title could be:

===========================================================
 Help a twitter account to increase its social media reach
===========================================================

This is for developers:

 * include TwitterTool via maven (see mvnrepo) or clone from here
 * set your customer token + secrect in the TwitterTooling class
 * search on the internet for some accounts you want to grab friends (or followers)
 * ready, set, SPAM!